     *   `<loc>`: The full URL of a page on your site.
     *   `<lastmod>`:  The date when the page was last modified (optional, but recommended). Use the format `YYYY-MM-DD`.
     *   `<changefreq>`:  How frequently the content on the URL is likely to change (options like `always`, `hourly`, `daily`, `weekly`, `monthly`, `yearly`, `never`).
     *   `<priority>`:  The relative priority of this URL compared to other URLs on your site (a value between `0.0` and `1.0`).  Homepage is usually `1.0`.